Ordering Data

   For now, to order LANDSAT data, go to EarthExplorer at the USGS/EROS
   Data Center.
   or
   Earth Observing System Data Gateway at the USGS/EROS Data Center.
   In the future, we will connect directly to the EarthExplorer Shopping
   Basket and the Data Gateway Shopping Basket from the USGS Browse Image
   Viewer.
